Package commands

package commands
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Add
    Command to build element and add it to collection.
    AddIfMax
    Command to build element and add it to collection if it is greater than any other.
    Clear
    Command to clear the collection.
    Command
    Abstract class for commands
    ExecuteScript
    Command to execute script from a file.
    Exit
    Command to exit the program.
    Help
    Command to show list of available commands.
    History
    Command to show previously executed commands.
    Info
    Command to show info about the collection.
    PrintFieldAscendingDifficulty
    Command to print element's difficulties in ascending order.
    PrintFieldDescendingAuthor
    Command to print element's authors in descending order.
    RemoveById
    Command to remove element from collection by its id.
    RemoveLower
    Command to remove every element from collection if it is lower than given.
    Save
    Command to save the collection to the file.
    Show
    Command to show collection elements.
    SumOfMinimalPoint
    Command to print sum of minimal points of every element.
    Update
    Command to update element in collection by its id.
